#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:222
msgid "Chieftain, dwarves surrounded us. They appeared out of nowhere."
msgstr "首领，我们被矮子包围了，他们到处都是！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:223
msgid "That was expected. We didn't fight them for a long time. Go to your post and start you war cry, trumpeter!"
msgstr "早料到了，咱们很久没打过他们了。号令手，快去吹战斗号！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:231
msgid "I have a bad feeling."
msgstr "我有不好的预感……"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:232
msgid "I am here with you, you don't need to worry."
msgstr "别担心，有我在呢。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:235
msgid "Well, we've surrounda' those pigs. It'a goodish time to slaught'a them. Pelamthas, show what ye've got."
msgstr "好，咱们包围了这群猪。现在宰了他们倍儿棒！佩莱姆萨斯，给看看你有啥好东西。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:236
msgid "Aye, milord. Read'ye! Aim! Fire!"
msgstr "哎好，大王。预备！对准了！点火！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:242
msgid "That was close."
msgstr "好险啊！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:244
msgid "Grandpa, why you didna' fire?"
msgstr "爷，你咋不开火呢？"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:245
msgid "I canna' figure out this thin'."
msgstr "我弄不懂这玩意儿。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:246
msgid "I've trained ya ..."
msgstr "我都教过你了呀……"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:255
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\13_blood_for_blood.cfg:353
msgid "Wake up warrior, or you will oversleep the battle!"
msgstr "勇士们醒醒，不然就睡过战斗了！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:256
msgid "Going to position, chief."
msgstr "马上到位，首领！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:262
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:278
msgid "Read'ye! Aim! Fire!"
msgstr "预备！瞄准！点火！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:271
msgid "Grandpa ... I willna' forgive myself ... "
msgstr "爷爷……我不会原谅自己的……"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:272
msgid "Pelamthas, it's a honour to di'ya on the battlefield. Your .. how you call them .. cannons - a' splendid! "
msgstr "佩莱姆萨斯，死在战场上是荣幸的事儿。你们的…你们管这些东西叫…大炮——啊太有才了！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:272
msgid "But they'r too valuable for an inept hands."
msgstr "但这玩意儿在笨蛋手里也太宝贝了。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:290
msgid "Ha-ha-ha, so much fun! Enough I thin', our man are approachin' their walls."
msgstr "哈-哈-哈，太好玩了！我觉嘀够了，咱们的人就到他们的城墙了！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:300
msgid "Hear'a the reinforcements. I've tired of waitin'."
msgstr "援军到地儿了。等他们真烦死我了。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:307
msgid "Hushnak, there are too many of them."
msgstr "哈什奈克，它们人太多了！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:308
msgid "Bart, I have a task for you."
msgstr "巴特，我交给你个任务！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:313
msgid "Waiting for your orders, chief Hushnak."
msgstr "听候命令，哈什奈克首领！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:314
msgid "To flee from the battlefield is unworthy of an orc. But my son is too small to fight. Take Rark and go to Glamdrol. You are responsible for his life. If you fail, I will find you even in hell."
msgstr "兽人不配逃出战场，但我儿子太小了不能打。带拉克去戈拉姆多！他的命就交给你了！要是你死了，我下地狱也要找你算账！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:315
msgid "Hushnak, Bart is our son's last hope. Send more riders to protect him."
msgstr "哈什奈克，巴特是我们儿子的最后希望！多派几个骑手保护他！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:316
msgid "Right."
msgstr "好！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:317
msgid "I have something for you, Bart. This amulet will help you. When Rark will grow up, tell him about us and give him this amulet."
msgstr "我还有东西给你，巴特。这个护身符能祝你一臂之力。等拉克长大了，告诉他我们的事情并给他这护身符。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:320
msgid "Thank you."
msgstr "多谢！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:321
msgid "I know their leader, his name is Uritbor. Remember that name. Now run, run faster than the wind!"
msgstr "我认识他们首领，他叫厄瑞特博。记着这个名字。现在快跑！得跑得比风还快！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:322
msgid "Chief, you can count on me. I will not fail."
msgstr "首领，交给我吧！我不会失败的！"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:332
msgid "Survive until Bart escapes to the sign in the south-western part of the map"
msgstr "活到巴特逃到地图西南角的标志处"

