#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:358
msgid "Hmm.. These orcs are fightin' like real berserks, but their end is nea'. My reinforcements are comin'."
msgstr "哼嗯…这些兽人打得跟真的狂战士一样，但他们很快就玩儿完。我的援军来了。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\01_the_hammer_and_the_anvil.cfg:372
