msgstr "本关结束时所有活狼都会跟着拉克并变忠诚。这是你唯一能征募狼的一关，以后就只能召回它们了。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\04_the_wolfs_lair.cfg:247
msgid "There is a hole leading to the wolf's lair, but it is too narrow for a human.."
msgstr "这儿有个通着狼窝的洞，但是太窄了，人钻不过去……"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\04_the_wolfs_lair.cfg:252
msgid "Hey, don't touch wolves. We have our own plans for them."
msgstr "嘿，别动那些狼，我们对他们有自己的打算。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\04_the_wolfs_lair.cfg:253
msgid "Hello, dear orcs. What plans do you have?"
msgstr "兽人朋友，你好啊。你有啥打算？"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\04_the_wolfs_lair.cfg:253
msgid "looks at Bart"
msgstr "看着巴特"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\04_the_wolfs_lair.cfg:253
msgid "I think I understood. Usually I sell a wolfskin for $gold_for_wolf gold. But for you, nice orcs, I will make a special offer. For the same price I will sell you two alive wolves. Just wait until we capture them. What do you think? It is a very good price!"
msgstr "哦我懂了，平时我一张狼皮卖$gold_for_wolf金币。但是对像你这样的好兽人，我特价卖你。同样的价格我卖你俩活狼。你就等我们抓住它们吧。咋样？这价格非常公道吧！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\04_the_wolfs_lair.cfg:254
msgid "I have a counter offer, kind skinners. Either you will get out of here quickly. Or I will skin you alive and feed it to the wolves. What do you think?"
msgstr "好一帮皮贩子，不过我提供相反服务。你可以赶紧走人，或者我活剥了你的皮喂狼。咋样？"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\04_the_wolfs_lair.cfg:255
msgid "We don't want troubles. We are merchants, not warriors. Though, as you could see, we are numerous and we can handle weapons."
msgstr "咱不是来找茬的。咱是生意人，不是打架的。你也得看看，我们人多还有家伙。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\04_the_wolfs_lair.cfg:256
msgid "Stop your politician speeches, Middry. I have never fight with an orc before. I wonder how strong their bones are and what is the color of their blood."
msgstr "梅德瑞，少跟他们扯犊子。我还没跟兽人打过呢。我想看看他们身子板有多结实，还有血是啥色儿的。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\04_the_wolfs_lair.cfg:257
msgid "You are a lucky orc, Rark. You either harden yourself in these clashes, or leave this world early. And the same will happen to all of us."
msgstr "拉克，你是个幸运的兽人。你可以选择在这些冲突中强化自己，也可能会早离开这个世界。我们跟你一起。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\04_the_wolfs_lair.cfg:258
msgid "This is my last proposition - three wolves for $gold_for_wolf gold."
msgstr "这是我最后出价了啊——$gold_for_wolf金币三匹狼！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\04_the_wolfs_lair.cfg:259
msgid "I will skin you for free. Orcs, show them no mercy!"
msgstr "我免费给你剥皮！弟兄们，斩尽杀绝，一个不留！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\04_the_wolfs_lair.cfg:268
msgid "These wolves are slightly different from mainline units. Pay attention to their ability. A wolf is stronger when there are other wolves next to it."
msgstr "这些狼与主线单位有点不同。请注意它们的能力，一匹狼在身旁有其他狼时会更强。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\04_the_wolfs_lair.cfg:273
msgid "We must save as many wolves as possible. They will become loyal and never leave us."
msgstr "我们能救多少狼就救多少，它们会忠于我们并且再也不走。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\04_the_wolfs_lair.cfg:289
msgid "Here you are, buddy."
msgstr "我来救你了，伙计。"

#. [event]: id=wolf_cant_release
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\04_the_wolfs_lair.cfg:307
msgid "Wolf tries to release its kind.. with no success."
msgstr "狼试着解救它的好…失败了。"

#. [floating_text]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\04_the_wolfs_lair.cfg:324
msgid "+$gold_for_wolf gold"
msgstr "+$gold_for_wolf金币"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\04_the_wolfs_lair.cfg:338
msgid "What a good business I had, these nasty orcs ruined everything."
msgstr "多好的生意啊，都让这些恶心的兽人毁了！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\04_the_wolfs_lair.cfg:354
msgid "Wolves are saved, we completed our mission."
msgstr "狼都救下来了，咱们完活了。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\04_the_wolfs_lair.cfg:411
msgid "That was their leader, we shouldn't have allowed his death."
msgstr "群狼无首了，我们不该让他死的。"

