msgstr "达克汗会掉落对用矛的单位有用的道具。"

#. [note]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\05_the_competition.cfg:408
msgid "Dhakhan's units require <b>30% less</b> experience than usual to advance."
msgstr "达克汗的单位需要比平常<b>少30%</b>的经验才能升级。"

#. [note]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\05_the_competition.cfg:411
msgid "Galatea's units require <b>30% more</b> experience than usual to advance."
msgstr "高拉提的单位需要比平常<b>多30%</b>的经验才能升级。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\05_the_competition.cfg:604
msgid "We are back and we want justice."
msgstr "我们回来讨回公道。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\05_the_competition.cfg:605
msgid "Dhakhan, didn't you pay nagas for this bay, as we agreed?"
msgstr "达克汗，你没按我们说好的向娜迦买了这个海湾吗？"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\05_the_competition.cfg:606
msgid "Madam, I paid them, as we agreed."
msgstr "我按咱说好的买了啊。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\05_the_competition.cfg:607
msgid "Amailis, what does it mean? They paid you for this territories? Don't try to fool us!"
msgstr "俄玫利斯，这什么意思？他们买了你这块地？别玩我们！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\05_the_competition.cfg:608
msgid "They paid us with their steel, not gold. And now we are here to pay them the same price."
msgstr "他们用铁买的，不是金子。所以现在我们一分不差地来还你们了。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\05_the_competition.cfg:609
msgid "You didn't give me a reason to doubt you. I expect you won't give any reasons in the future as well."
msgstr "我现在没理由怀疑你，我希望你以后也别有理由让我怀疑你。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\05_the_competition.cfg:610
msgid "Madam, don't listen to nagas, they are liars."
msgstr "长官，别听娜迦的，他们是骗子！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\05_the_competition.cfg:611
msgid "Dhakhan, we will continue this conversation later. Now we have to defend ourselves."
msgstr "达克汗，这事儿我们以后再议。现在我们得自卫！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\05_the_competition.cfg:612
msgid "Yes, madam!"
msgstr "是，长官！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\05_the_competition.cfg:613
msgid "I am not sure they will have a chance to continue this conversation."
msgstr "我可不确定他们还有机会接着讨论。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\05_the_competition.cfg:622
msgid "Chief Erurag, we came under your command by order of Amailis. We know this bay and will give you any help you need."
msgstr "俄如莱格首领，我们奉俄玫利斯之命听候您的命令。我们了解这个海湾而且能祝你们一臂之力。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\05_the_competition.cfg:623
msgid "Excellent, your help will be handy."
msgstr "好，你们肯定能帮上忙。"

