msgstr "俄如莱格，我感激你。为表谢意，我给你这把只有最强的武士才能用的剑。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:364
msgid "Hint: This is the last scenario with Erurag. It may be wiser to give this sword to another unit."
msgstr "提示：这是俄如莱格出场的最后一关。把这把剑给其他单位更明智。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:366
msgid "Excellent. This is a good place for a camp. We can cut some wood and hunt animals while those cowards are trembling behind the walls."
msgstr "很好。这是个扎营的好地方。咱可以趁这些懦夫在墙后面颤抖的时候打打猎，砍砍树。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:367
msgid "Those dirty orcs will kill my forest, I will not allow that to happen."
msgstr "这帮下流的兽人会杀了我的森林，我绝不能容忍。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:368
msgid "It seems there are not so many of them. What do you think, Delithrar? This may be a good opportunity for our men to get a battle experience."
msgstr "看起来他们不多。戴立萨拉，你怎么看？这或许会是个让咱们的人得到战斗经验的好机会。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:369
msgid "I agree. Warriors and mages, go outside the wall and feed those marauders with arrows and fireballs."
msgstr "我同意。勇士们，法师们，到墙外用弓箭和火球招待这些强盗去！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:370
