#. [note]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:478
msgid "In this scenario each village provides upkeep support for 3 unit levels. Village income is 1 gold as usual."
msgstr "这一关里每个村庄能为单位提供三级的维护费用。村庄收入照常为1金币。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:582
msgid "Piece of cake. What is the point of an unbreakable wall if you have such flimsy backdoor?"
msgstr "小菜一碟。有这么个破后门还要刀枪不入的墙干嘛？"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:632
msgid "We need to release the prisoner, she may help us."
msgstr "咱得把囚徒放出来，她也许能帮我们。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:658
msgid "There is one more prisoner."
msgstr "这儿还有个囚徒。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:684
msgid "Orcs?"
msgstr "兽人？"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:685
msgid "Have you waited for someone else here?"
msgstr "你在这儿等过其他人吗？"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:686
msgid "Anyway that's good you are here."
msgstr "不管是谁，还好你来救我了。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:687
msgid "And how did you get here?"
msgstr "你是怎么进来的？"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:688
msgid "That mage.. He hurt a woman, who hired me to shorten his ... life. But I was captured and thrown in this cage."
msgstr "那个法师…他伤了一个雇我让他短命的女人，但我被抓住并被扔到了这个监牢里。"

#. [then]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:692
msgid "We have already defeated him."
msgstr "我们已经干掉他了。"

#. [then]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:693
msgid "I hope it was a painful death."
msgstr "我希望他死得很痛苦。"

#. [else]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:697
msgid "Now you have a chance to finish your job."
msgstr "现在你有机会完成工作了。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:725
msgid "I am so glad you released me."
msgstr "非常感谢你救了我。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:726
msgid "Why are you imprisoned here?"
msgstr "你是怎么被抓到这儿的？"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:727
msgid "I was one of Aethuc's students. But I have some unpopular talents, you know.."
msgstr "我是艾萨克的一名学生。但我有些不光彩的才能，你懂的……"

#. [then]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:744
msgid "Let me show you."
msgstr "我给你看看。"

#. [then]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:752
msgid "Warrior, rise and fight!"
msgstr "勇士，起来战斗吧！"

#. [then]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:763
msgid "Wow! That's impressive!"
msgstr "哇哦！太惊人了！"

#. [else]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:766
msgid "Necromancy, I see."
msgstr "妖法，我懂了。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:770
msgid "Will you join us?"
msgstr "你跟我们走不？"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:771
msgid "You saved my life. Be good to me and I won't leave you."
msgstr "你救了我的命，对我有恩，我跟着你。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:772
msgid "Nessa is a new hero in your team. Don't let her die."
msgstr "奈萨是你的一个新英雄单位，别让她死了。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:804
msgid "What? Guard, attack the intruders. They have fooled us, I will personally slain them!"
msgstr "什么？卫兵，打入侵者！我们中计了，我要亲自杀了他们！"

#. [event]: id=mage_merudda_fight
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:845
msgid "Merudda, I asked you to forgive me a thousand times.."
msgstr "么鲁达，我已经一千次请你原谅我了……"

#. [event]: id=mage_merudda_fight
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:846
msgid "This is the last time, you villain."
msgstr "这就是最后一次了，你个坏蛋。"

#. [event]: id=mage_merudda_fight
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:847
msgid "Now I see who is that woman who hired her."
msgstr "现在我知道是谁雇的她了。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:855
msgid "What a pity. Nagas can count on me, now I am their leader."
msgstr "真遗憾。娜迦能指望我，现在我是他们的首领了。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:873
msgid "Is this the end?"
msgstr "我这就完了吗？"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:874
msgid "No doubts, buddy."
msgstr "没错，小家伙。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:887
msgid "Look, the wall has fallen!"
msgstr "快看，墙消失了！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:895
msgid "I shouldn't have left my village. What a dishonourable death. A miserable mercenary ... "
msgstr "我不该离开我的村子的。我一个悲苦的雇佣兵，死得憋屈啊…"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:906
msgid "The stronghold is ours! I am proud of you Rark."
msgstr "要塞归我们了！拉克我替你自豪！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\06_the_backdoor.cfg:975
msgid "We shouldn't have allowed this to happen."
msgstr "我们不该让这事儿发生的。"

