#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\10_the_flaming_stone.cfg:368
msgid "Trolls are fighting with drakes. We can get allies here."
msgstr "巨魔们在跟龙人打。咱们能在这儿得到盟友。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\10_the_flaming_stone.cfg:369
msgid "Hi, trolls. Do you need help?"
msgstr "嗨，巨魔。要帮忙吗？"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\10_the_flaming_stone.cfg:370
msgid "Yes. Trolls in troubles. Dwarves attacked and killed many trolls, beasts with wings attacked trolls."
msgstr "对。巨魔有困难。矮子打杀了很多巨魔，长翅膀的野兽打了巨魔。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\10_the_flaming_stone.cfg:371
msgid "Dwarves killed many trolls?"
msgstr "矮子杀了很多巨魔？"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\10_the_flaming_stone.cfg:372
msgid "Trolls and dwarves neighbours, lived in the caves. Dwarves found gems in troll's cave. Dwarves banished trolls. Trolls went to the surface. Beasts with wings attacked trolls."
msgstr "巨魔和矮子邻居，住洞里。矮子在巨魔洞里找到了宝石。矮子赶跑了巨魔。巨魔到了地表。长翅膀的野兽打了巨魔。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\10_the_flaming_stone.cfg:373
msgid "Drakes."
msgstr "龙人。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\10_the_flaming_stone.cfg:374
msgid "Do you know a dwarf named Uritbor?"
msgstr "你知道一个叫厄瑞特博的矮子吗？"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\10_the_flaming_stone.cfg:375
msgid "Uritbor dwarvish king banished trolls."
msgstr "厄瑞特博矮子王赶走了巨魔。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\10_the_flaming_stone.cfg:376
msgid "We are here to find and kill him. I offer you to go back to the cave and defeat dwarves together."
msgstr "我们来这儿找他，然后杀了他。我帮你回洞里一起干掉矮子。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\10_the_flaming_stone.cfg:377
msgid "Dak agree."
msgstr "达克同意。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\10_the_flaming_stone.cfg:378
msgid "Drakes will not let us go."
msgstr "龙人不会让我们走的。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\10_the_flaming_stone.cfg:379
msgid "Drakes, do you agree to stop this senseless slaughter? Trolls will go to their cave."
msgstr "龙人，你同意停止没意义的屠杀吗？巨魔要回他们的洞里。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\10_the_flaming_stone.cfg:380
msgid "They have killed my people. The will answer for this crime."
msgstr "他们杀了我的人民。他们必须给我个交代。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\10_the_flaming_stone.cfg:381
msgid "Dak smashed beasts."
msgstr "达克砸了野兽。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\10_the_flaming_stone.cfg:382
msgid "We are in a difficult situation, Rark. Drakes are numerous. Their villages are located high in the mountains, it would be difficult to capture and hold them."
msgstr "拉克，我们现在处境艰难。龙人很多。他们的村子在高山上，抓住并看住他们可不容易。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\10_the_flaming_stone.cfg:383
msgid "Drake, this is the last time I am offering truce. Agree or you will regret."
msgstr "龙人，这是我给你的最后一次停战机会了。要么同意，要么你会后悔的。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\10_the_flaming_stone.cfg:384
msgid "Orcs, if you will help the trolls, we will attack you too."
msgstr "兽人，你要是帮巨魔，我们就连你们一起打！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\10_the_flaming_stone.cfg:385
msgid "I will burn your villages and enslave their inhabitants. It will make you change your mind."
msgstr "我要烧了你们的村子，抓你们的村民作奴隶。这样你会改变主意的。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\10_the_flaming_stone.cfg:393
msgid "You think you can beat me?"
msgstr "你以为你能打败我？"

#. [floating_text]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\10_the_flaming_stone.cfg:463
msgid "+2 gold"
msgstr "+2金币"

#. [do]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\10_the_flaming_stone.cfg:500
