msgstr "这个奴隶回到了你的手里。"

#. [floating_text]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\10_the_flaming_stone.cfg:585
msgid "trained"
msgstr "训练完毕"

#. [event]: id=drake_leader_trains_speech
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\10_the_flaming_stone.cfg:599
msgid "You are free now. I will teach you to fight, then go back to the battlefield."
msgstr "你现在自由了。我教你怎么战斗，然后你回战场去。"

#. [event]: id=drake_slave_trained_speech
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\10_the_flaming_stone.cfg:605
msgid "Thank you, Gelslar Elch. I will fight the marauders!"
msgstr "谢谢你，盖斯拉奥尺。我要打入侵者！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\10_the_flaming_stone.cfg:615
msgid "I am mighty Gelslar Elch, I can't be defeated."
msgstr "我是盖斯拉奥尺，我无人能敌。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\10_the_flaming_stone.cfg:616
msgid "Anyone can be defeated."
msgstr "谁都能被打败。"

#. [event]: id=check_victory_condition
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\10_the_flaming_stone.cfg:630
msgid "What do you say now, drake? Should we continue? We could let these slaves go in exchange for a pass."
msgstr "小龙，你现在想不想说什么？我们要不要接着来？我们也可以用这些奴隶当过路费。"

#. [event]: id=check_victory_condition
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\10_the_flaming_stone.cfg:631
msgid "I agree, let them go."
msgstr "好吧，放他们走。"

#. [event]: id=check_victory_condition
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\10_the_flaming_stone.cfg:632
msgid "Thank you, wise Gelslar Elch."
msgstr "谢谢，英明的盖斯拉奥尺。"

#. [event]: id=check_victory_condition
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\10_the_flaming_stone.cfg:633
msgid "Orcs helped trolls. Now go to the caves."
msgstr "兽人帮了巨魔，现在去洞穴。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\10_the_flaming_stone.cfg:659
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:953
