#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:724
msgid "Dwarves in our home. Strange runes. Dwarves must leave."
msgstr "矮人在我们家。奇怪的符文。矮人必须滚。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:725
msgid "And then we will go for Uritbor."
