#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:726
msgid "Yes."
msgstr "好。"

#. [message]: speaker=nuk_gah
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:729
msgid "Trolls are very thankful to you Rark. Please accept this gift, it is a regeneration potion."
msgstr "拉克，巨魔们非常感激你。请收下这个礼物，这是瓶自愈药水。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:740
msgid "Thank you, Nuk Gah."
msgstr "谢谢你，纳克伽。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:747
msgid "They are here."
msgstr "他们来了。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:749
msgid "Rark, we were waiting for you."
msgstr "拉克，我们一直在等你"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:750
msgid "I hear strange voices in my head."
msgstr "我脑袋里有奇怪的说话声。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:751
msgid "We want to help you, Rark. You must believe us, otherwise we won't have enough strength to do anything."
msgstr "我们想帮你，拉克。你一定要相信我们，不然我们没有能力帮忙。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:752
msgid "Is this a nightmare again? These voices are making me insane."
msgstr "又是噩梦吗？这声音好难受啊！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:753
msgid "Rark all right?"
msgstr "拉克好吗？"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:754
msgid "Son, do you believe us?"
msgstr "儿子，你相信我们吗？"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:755
msgid "I hear something too. Distant woman's voice said <i>son</i> and <i>believe</i>."
msgstr "我也听到了什么。远处有女人的声音说“儿子”和“相信”。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:756
msgid "I believe you, mother."
msgstr "我相信你，娘。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:762
msgid "We knew that one day you would come to avenge us."
msgstr "我们知道总有一天你会为我们报仇的。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:763
msgid "When you will face the dwarf, we will be there to help you."
msgstr "当你见到那个矮子时，我们会去帮你。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:773
msgid "And one more thing. All those years my friend Vrugdish was imprisoned. Release him. He is in bad condition, yet still able to fight."
msgstr "还有，这些年以来我的朋友瓦格迪什被关着。放他出来吧，他现在状况不好，但还能战斗。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:774
msgid "Arrgh. Go away ghost."
msgstr "啊。鬼快滚！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:775
msgid "We will be waiting for you, Rark."
msgstr "拉克，我们等着你。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:776
msgid "I hope you are real."
msgstr "我希望你们是真的。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:788
msgid "We have guests!"
msgstr "咱们有客人了！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:789
