#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:848
msgid "Dak?"
msgstr "达克？"

#. [event]: id=release_rocklobber
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:849
msgid "Yes. Dak here, take caves for trolls."
msgstr "对。达克这里，为巨魔拿下洞穴。"

#. [event]: id=release_rocklobber
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:850
msgid "Thur with you. Dwarves can't capture Thur again!"
msgstr "萨跟你一块儿。矮子再也抓不住萨了！"

#. [event]: id=release_whelp
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:865
msgid "Borb is free! Borb fight dwarves!"
msgstr "鲍勃自由了！鲍勃打矮子！"

#. [event]: id=release_warlord
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:880
msgid "Go away ghost."
msgstr "鬼走开！"

#. [event]: id=release_warlord
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:881
msgid "Vrugdish, we are not ghosts. Many years have passed, but I am here to defeat dwarves. My name is Rark, I am son of Hushnak and Vadasha."
msgstr "瓦格迪什，我们不是鬼。这么多年过去了，但我来这儿杀矮子了。我叫拉克，是哈什奈克和瓦达莎的儿子啊。"

#. [event]: id=release_warlord
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:882
msgid "I can not believe it."
msgstr "我不信。"

#. [event]: id=release_warlord
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:883
msgid "Can you fight?"
msgstr "你还能打吗？"

#. [event]: id=release_warlord
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\11_greediness.cfg:885
msgid "Vrugdish, can you fight?"
msgstr "瓦格迪什，你还能战斗吗？"

#. [event]: id=release_warlord
