msgstr "死去的兽人们都想要矮子们的鲜血。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\13_blood_for_blood.cfg:300
msgid "Orcs, trolls and even undead are agains' me. Pelalis, go for reinforcement."
msgstr "兽人、巨魔，甚至亡灵都来跟我对着干了。佩莱利斯，去搬救兵！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\13_blood_for_blood.cfg:301
msgid "On my way!"
msgstr "这就去！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\13_blood_for_blood.cfg:312
