msgstr "格摩德瑞斯，你去叫我们的大伙计。就说大战要爆发了。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\13_blood_for_blood.cfg:313
msgid "Yes, my king."
msgstr "是，大王。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\13_blood_for_blood.cfg:326
msgid "I recognise you, Dak. You stupid cowar', dare to come here with a bunch of stinking dead slugs."
msgstr "我认出你来了，达克。你个胆小鬼懦夫，竟敢带一群臭死鼻涕虫来这里？"

#. [event]
