msgstr "然后呢？恁朋友是谁啊？"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\13_blood_for_blood.cfg:329
msgid "My name is Rark. A long time ago you slaughtered my tribe in the Heart Mountains."
msgstr "我是拉克。很久以前你们屠杀了我在心之山脉的部落。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\13_blood_for_blood.cfg:330
msgid "Boy, my axe is the last thin' so many orcs have seen in their paltry lives. I don' remember your tribe. No doubt I gave them what they deserved."
msgstr "小子，我的斧头是很多兽人不值钱的命里看见的最后的东西。我不记得你的部落，不过我肯定给了他们报应。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\13_blood_for_blood.cfg:331
msgid "Why don't you answer him, master of threat?"
msgstr "你怎么不告诉他，威慑王？"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\13_blood_for_blood.cfg:332
msgid "Swords and bows will be my answer. Orcs, trolls, all who are here with me. I will not promise that you will survive this day. I promise you - there are enough dwarves for all of you. Show them what you're made of! Crash their bones, tear them apart, bathe in their blood!"
msgstr "我马上就用剑和弓告诉他。兽人们，巨魔们，所有跟我一起的弟兄们，我不保证你们能活过今天，但我能向你们保证——这的矮子绝对够你们宰的。让他们知道我们可是吃肉的！砸烂他们的骨头，把他们分尸，还得用他们的血洗澡！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\13_blood_for_blood.cfg:333
