msgid ""
"The First Dark Age of Wesnoth. Orcs are aggressively increasing their power on the Great Continent. However, not all of their campaigns were successful. You will witness the disastrous one. A small orcish settlement in the Heart Mountains is attacked by superior dwarvish forces. Orcs are doomed to be exterminated. Play this campaign and take part in the further story.\n"
"(Hard level, 12 scenarios)"
msgstr ""
"在韦诺的第一个黑暗时代，兽人们通过侵略来增强他们在泰陆的势力。可是，他们不是百战百胜的。你将看到一幕惨重的情景：在心之山脉的一处小兽人居民地遭到了超强矮人军团的攻击，那些兽人注定要被灭亡……请玩这个战役来演绎后来的故事。\n"
"（困难级别，12幕场景）"

